come rain , come shine ( hangul : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ; rr : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ; literally " i love you , i love you not " ) is a 2011 south korean film by lee &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . a young woman ( im &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) informs her husband of five years ( hyun bin ) that she is leaving him for another man ( ha jung-woo ) , but the husband remains calm and even helps her pack . the experimental film traces in real-time parts of their last three hours together while the wife prepares to move out . the film premiered in competition at the 61st berlin international film festival in 2011 .